  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Production (video)</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">The following is a short introduction to Data &amp; More Production overview</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>The Production overview provides an overview of 2 different things:&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"123\" style=\"width: 47px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png?width=47&amp;height=123&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png\" width=\"47\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png?width=24&amp;height=62&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png 24w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png?width=47&amp;height=123&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png 47w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png?width=71&amp;height=185&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png 71w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png?width=94&amp;height=246&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png 94w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png?width=118&amp;height=308&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png 118w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png?width=141&amp;height=369&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-53-5580-PM.png 141w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 47px) 100vw, 47px\"><br>1.<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;An overview of all the clean-up report sent outs. It is possible to see</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;when reports where sent out, who got the report, who did not get a report and if a user for some reason does not have the e-mail with a link to their clean-up report it is possible to copy their link and send it to them again.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>2. An overview of all the different sources, how much data has been index per user per source&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In the following video there is an introduction to the Production overview</p>\n<div class=\"hs-video-widget\" data-hsv-embed-id=\"eb966207-9469-45cf-930d-a451bfe139d2\">\n  <div class=\"hs-video-container\" style=\"max-width: 688px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n    <div class=\"hs-video-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; height: 0; padding-bottom: 49.27%\">\n      <iframe data-hsv-src=\"https://play.hubspotvideo.com/v/4381120/id/99898367803\" referrerpolicy=\"origin\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen;\" style=\"position: absolute !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; left: 0; top: 0; border: 0 none; pointer-events: initial\" title=\"HubSpot Video\" loading=\"lazy\" data-hsv-id=\"99898367803\" data-hsv-style=\"\" data-hsv-width=\"688\" data-hsv-height=\"339\" data-hsv-autoplay=\"false\" data-hsv-loop=\"false\" data-hsv-muted=\"false\" data-hsv-hidden-controls=\"false\" data-hsv-full-width=\"false\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Explanation to the different states in the Mail sources:</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"30\" style=\"width: 688px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/yUiDOmSbcjthUs_XQuaoaHyx6I7JblCIi5ROO55_QOmjGKSwEykhJUL6w5aXputJAtHxfuVDlW15w_V3Z4pStcZvrauhS6jQT4VDCTZ9ONyKzNLPNfITo-5oWK2g8QRyG02QF7_FTa9ziBnqnxXvbV0\" width=\"688\"></p>\n<p><strong>All</strong> : The total number of licensed users in the account<br><strong>Ready</strong>: Ready for send out - (pending accounts can also be ready for send out if they are scanned more that one time)</p>\n<p><strong>Processing</strong>: The accounts are currently being processed</p>\n<p><strong>Pending</strong>: The account is waiting to be processed - or processed again.</p>\n<p><strong>Pause</strong>: The account is paused, and no new data will be processed</p>\n<p><strong>Missing</strong>: Accounts that have not yet been processed - but will be</p>\n<p><strong>Disabled</strong>: The account has been disabled, and all data have been removed from the DMCS</p>\n<p><strong>Error</strong>: MS don't allow the DMCS to read data on the specific account.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"273\" style=\"width: 688px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/I29XsQoy3WZtqEOxlnDr3n5ha3bLh9fH9wdtS5h8Ljxbr9y56XYkVSEulyG6qpi4RCleI07wVHagg5l-AgIjpzwdSl1IX8V8NS1qgvXdY3DXTMnpTuUDqvhnejj2N6S6a5zSI6bC6nHd-zaeVMyZ7iA\" width=\"688\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Approx. Total MSG: The number of messages identified by MS Graph</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Scanned messages: The number of messages scanned by DMCS</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Scanned document: The number of documents scanned by DMCS (including attachments and pictures)</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Latest: The latest time the account was fully scanned</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Status:&nbsp;</li>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"2\">Error: Account cant me read</li>\n<li aria-level=\"2\">Missing: The account have not been scanned yet</li>\n<li aria-level=\"2\">Active: The account has an active licence and will be scanned in due time</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/compliance-dashboard"
}